        "timestamp": "2021-11-30 10:10:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHere is the diff between master and istanbul. To apply to Jakarta.\n\ncedric@dev:~/Devs/ONAP/doc/examples/sphinx$ diff -urN istanbul/ master/\ndiff -urN istanbul/conf.py master/conf.py\n--- istanbul/conf.py\t2021-11-30 11:07:46.266894536 +0100\n+++ master/conf.py\t2021-11-30 11:07:46.266894536 +0100\n@@ -1,6 +1,6 @@\n from docs_conf.conf import *\n \n-branch = 'istanbul'\n+branch = 'latest'\n master_doc = 'index'\n \n linkcheck_ignore = [\ndiff -urN istanbul/conf.yaml master/conf.yaml\n--- istanbul/conf.yaml\t2021-11-30 11:07:46.266894536 +0100\n+++ master/conf.yaml\t2021-11-30 11:07:46.266894536 +0100\n@@ -3,5 +3,5 @@\n project: onap\n \n # Change this to ReleaseBranchName to modify the header\n-default-version: istanbul\n+default-version: latest\n #\ndiff -urN istanbul/tox.ini master/tox.ini\n--- istanbul/tox.ini\t2021-11-30 11:07:46.266894536 +0100\n+++ master/tox.ini\t2021-11-30 11:07:46.266894536 +0100\n@@ -7,8 +7,8 @@\n basepython = python3\n deps =\n     -r{toxinidir}/requirements-docs.txt\n-    -chttps://git.onap.org/doc/plain/etc/upper-constraints.os.txt?h=istanbul\n-    -chttps://git.onap.org/doc/plain/etc/upper-constraints.onap.txt?h=istanbul\n+    -chttps://git.onap.org/doc/plain/etc/upper-constraints.os.txt?h=master\n+    -chttps://git.onap.org/doc/plain/etc/upper-constraints.onap.txt?h=master\n commands =\n     sphinx-build -W -b html -n -d {envtmpdir}/doctrees ./ {toxinidir}/_build/html\n     echo \"Generated docs available in {toxinidir}/_build/html\"\n@@ -19,7 +19,7 @@\n basepython = python3\n deps =\n     -r{toxinidir}/requirements-docs.txt\n-    -chttps://git.onap.org/doc/plain/etc/upper-constraints.os.txt?h=istanbul\n-    -chttps://git.onap.org/doc/plain/etc/upper-constraints.onap.txt?h=istanbul\n+    -chttps://git.onap.org/doc/plain/etc/upper-constraints.os.txt?h=master\n+    -chttps://git.onap.org/doc/plain/etc/upper-constraints.onap.txt?h=master\n commands =\n     sphinx-build -W -b linkcheck -d {envtmpdir}/doctrees ./ {toxinidir}/_build/linkcheck",
